{"tid":1683170,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日跳閘差啲俾狗咬","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:36:11.000Z","uid":232531,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"423106c6a64ccccc56f4531524a88c47d1b6eba6","tid":1683170,"uid":232531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"今日喺大水坑站有六~七隻狗形foodpanda<br />\n<br />\n我平時見到foodpanda都唔多理會照跳<br />\n<br />\n咁今次一跳出閘隻foodpanda即刻四隻腳起勢咁跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就心知不妙諗住跑走, 點知跑到去樓梯位隻狗竟然起腳想kick低我等我碌落樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩我身手好冇俾佢kick到失平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後另外一隻狗就係咁喺後面講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係喇係喇, 師兄行路小心啲啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以各位手足跳閘要小心啲,唔好掉以輕心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次開post唔知開咩台先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b2f3686644454062a7f5f09134a0f971de95cc","tid":1683170,"uid":50521,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"好身手!!!"},{"pid":"39f9fe3541cebd84673741bb6a69df15d10bf4d6","tid":1683170,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"用綠卡啦"},{"pid":"6068b2a33f238cebbd7f4b17860b83426cbe13bb","tid":1683170,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acaf936226a9925a94f2d59d36f17727e5ca4958","tid":1683170,"uid":335834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:54:54.000Z","msg":"即係kick鳩完你就冇再追你？"},{"pi